Title: Small-Scale Self-Focusing Suppression at Intense Laser Beams in Mediums with Quadratic and Cubic Nonlinearity

Abstract: Method of small-scale self-focusing suppression at intense laser beams (1รท4TW/cm2) was developed and verified in experiments successfully. The theoretical model of plane wave instability in mediums with quadratic and cubic nonlinearity was created.
